---
title: Cal Smart Sesame Pork Bowls with Cilantro Rice
description: This Korean-inspired rice bowl is packed with veggies, cilantro-spiked rice and seasoned pork. Finish it with a spicy-sweet sesame sauce, then stir all these vibrant ingredients together for an unforgettable flavour experience.

